 | doi         = 10.1146/annurev.biochem.69.1.617
 | pmid        = 10966471
 | pmc         = 
}}</ref> et les [[ribosome]]s<ref name="10.1146/annurev.biochem.70.1.415">
{{Article
 | langue      = en
 | nom1        = Marina V. Rodnina et Wolfgang Wintermeyer
 | titre       = Fidelity of aminoacyl-tRNA selection on the ribosome: kinetic and structural mechanisms
 | périodique  = Annual Reviews Biochemistry
